You need to debug this piece of code. One way to do that is to break up the complexity and reduce the repetition by assigning intermediate results to their own variables:
```
char firstChar = sb.charAt(m.start());
if (Character.isUpperCase(firstChar)) {
    char lowerChar = Character.toLowerCase(firstChar);
    sb.setCharAt(m.start(), lowerChar);
} else {
